        <updateDate>2021-03-17T14:04:47Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>District of Columbia National Guard Home Rule Act </b> </p> <p>This bill makes the Mayor of the District of Columbia, rather than the President of the United States, the Commander-in-Chief of the National Guard of the District of Columbia.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
